Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Event>
    public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Event>, java.io.Serializable
    This class represents an Event object. An Event can have a name, speaker, time, duration(in hours), room, and set of attendees attending.
    See Also:
